{"tid":1817121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好攪到迷你倉","createTime":"2020-01-08T20:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T23:55:51.000Z","uid":26770,"like":28,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a91ca053206058e4c266ae35f3e0ac86050d10da","tid":1817121,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T20:08:01.000Z","msg":"雖然有人指某迷你倉篤灰,<ins>但正確做法係幫區內非藍倉谷生意而唔係攪人</ins><br />\n<br />\n大把人的cd,相等有紀念價值的野(先人遺物,diy野,書)係迷你倉<br />\n<br />\n迷你倉係絕對唔會賠,都絕對賠唔起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">裝修銀行,食肆就對普通客無影響直接對準公司<br />\n<strong>郁迷你倉係攬9平民,記住抗爭者佔主流民意</strong></span>"},{"pid":"591ed8199f8ca2ec790f56d466061d1a1a90ac17","tid":1817121,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T20:09:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">裝修銀行,食肆就對普通客無影響直接對準公司所以黃絲唔割<br />\n郁迷你倉係<span style=\"color: violet;\">棟</span>9平民</span>"},{"pid":"557e2e89632b12e9473d7e9a04e0f1271fd6d706","tid":1817121,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T20:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d7d0c4d8c9fabc7dbd6f2a8c5041101b317c4f","tid":1817121,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T20:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b08126fb48247fdab63e53c1fbd8d5e9d93051","tid":1817121,"uid":175346,"like":0,"